analysis.description:
Trade.contractBuyTokens (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#221-234) sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- msg.sender.transfer(valueETH) (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#233)

Trade.contractBuyTokensFrom (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#234-253) sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- from.transfer(valueETH) (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#248)

Trade.contractSellTokens (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#208-221) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-IERC20(tokenAddress).transfer(msg.sender,amount) (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#219-220)

Trade.contractBuyTokens (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#221-234) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-IERC20(tokenAddress).transferTrade(msg.sender,this,amount) (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#232-233)

Trade.contractBuyTokensFrom (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#234-253) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-IERC20(tokenAddress).transferTrade(from,this,amount) (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#247)

Trade.withdrawTokens (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#258-269) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-IERC20(tokenAddress).transferTrade(this,to,value) (/unique_chucks/11/0xc1759d97e0f1ca05fbfa4af0bbf55535c8a192dd.sol#265-266)
